snippet.title: [GZDoom] Hunter's Moon - Map Pack 0.4 Trailer
snippet.description:
Following the little but clear feedback of the 0.3 map pack, this time things will be different.

This new version of the map pack discards Baerhon's Lair Part 1 and Part 2, renews Rarlocan Main Base completely and finally makes use of the previously "hidden" Hub map. In addition new maps reusing few rooms replaces the discarded ones and other ones completely made from scratch will debut in this version.

ModDB Page: https://www.moddb.com/mods/hunters-moon
Discord Server: https://discord.gg/V9caq6W
